Title: Checkmk Docker container: Comment myhostname in /etc/postfix/main.cf
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: omd
Date: 1657569354
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0b1

This werk comments myhostname in /etc/postfix/main.cf.
Some mailservers reject mails with BOGUS HELO if you let myhostname uncommented.

